==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Open verdict
<hw>Open verdict</hw>. <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A verdict on a preliminary
investigation, finding the fact of a crime but not stating the criminal,
or finding the fact of a violent death without disclosing the
cause.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Openwork</ent>⟦br⟧
